{"tid":2182631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每次岀去嘅手足留意","createTime":"2020-08-31T12:22:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T22:47:57.000Z","uid":22837,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0079c642f7aeb0539caf295de95f04f199725379","tid":2182631,"uid":22837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T12:22:13.000Z","msg":"頭先係太子站附近見到有人偷拍，佢係見到著住深色衫嘅人就會影，路過放狗嘅都會影 (當然有影埋我)<br />\n<br />\n我係有當面屌柒佢，同埋睇住佢del咗相關嘅相，不過我估計佢已經影咗好多手足嘅大頭<br />\n<br />\n無錯，佢有權唔del相或者比人揭穿咗之後直接跑走<br />\n<br />\n但我希望岀得去行街嘅手足，打醒十二分精神，除咗留意狗之外，多啲留意身邊事同人，每一個小動作，你唔知會有咩影響<br />\n<br />\n見到類似依啲事，請你岀聲，唔洗怕柒<br />\n<br />\n因為你愈大聲咁屌，自然會有人過黎幫你<br />\n<br />\n香港人 爭氣"},{"pid":"1181b18ac74352954a7e931b8efd1eea3e045f34","tid":2182631,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T12:23:56.000Z","msg":"每個人身邊都有國安<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4c302a9b22a908bb04ab55dcddc236e5f0c958","tid":2182631,"uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1181b18ac74352954a7e931b8efd1eea3e045f34","tid":2182631,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T12:23:56.000Z","msg":"每個人身邊都有國安<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T12:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLHXJen.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLHXJen.gif&h=6f0d3a7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid